stories.title: The Indians have to get the right formula
stories.summary:
The decision of promoting Rahul Dravid to open the innings came as a
sort of a bolt from the blue at a time when the middle order needed to
retain all the strength it could muster intact

stories.title: India pip Zimbabwe in tense clash by 13 runs
stories.summary: Zimbabwe made their victory charge just a little too late, losing by 13 runs to India, their second successive defeat in the Champions Trophy in Sharjah
